# Super Admin Order Details

This rule documents the fields and data sources shown on the Super Admin order details page.

## Fields Rendered

- Exact timestamps: `createdAt`, `updatedAt`, `Date` (order date)
- Payment gateway: last transaction's `payment_gateway.Title`
- Address: `order.delivery_address` â†’ `FullAddress` + `shipping_city.Title` + `shipping_province.Title`
- Postal code: `delivery_address.PostalCode`
- Phone number: `user.Phone`
- Contract status and financials (subtotal/total shown via footer component)

## API Population

Populate parameters used when fetching the order:

```
populate[0]=user
populate[1]=contract
populate[2]=order_items
populate[3]=shipping
populate[4]=order_items.product_variation.product.CoverImage
populate[5]=order_items.product_color
populate[6]=order_items.product_size
populate[7]=user.user_info
populate[8]=delivery_address.shipping_city.shipping_province
populate[9]=contract.contract_transactions.payment_gateway
```

Endpoint: `GET /orders/:id`

## Gateway Logs

- Logs are retrieved from: `GET /order-logs?filters[order][id][$eq]=:orderId&sort[0]=createdAt:asc`
- UI component: `components/SuperAdmin/Order/GatewayLogs.tsx`
- Shows Description, Changes (JSON), and Jalali timestamp

## Checkout Address Capture

- Frontend submits `addressId` in finalize request
- Backend saves it on the order as `delivery_address`
